            "title": "港股開升53點  泡泡瑪特挫逾6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指開報23291，升53點或0.23% ; 恒生科技指數開報5103，升15點或0.3% ; 恒生國企指數開升18點或0.22%，報8429點。    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交28.84億元。   </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)續捱沽，跌6.2%，報233.2元，成交第四位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)升1.31%，報504.5元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升0.91%，報111元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">翰森製藥(03692)挫3.24%，報26.85元，表現最差藍籌股 ; 舜宇(02382)升2.16%，報64元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海天味業(03288)報36.3元，跌0.55%，險守招股價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">吉利(00175)升1.01%，報16元。</p>\n</div>",
